  "instructions": [
    "Marinate the beef with soy sauce, garlic, ginger, and cornstarch for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Heat a wok or large skillet over high heat. Add sesame oil if using. Stir-fry marinated beef until golden brown, set aside.",
